Pro Lag Destroyer v2 (Cleaner Windows & AI/Edge removal)

# Lag Destroyer v2 - Cleaner Windows & AI/Edge Remover

This advanced script removes Windows 11 bloatware including AI features like Copilot and Microsoft Edge, cleans leftover files and registry entries,  
and disables additional background processes that are not useful for gaming or performance.

### Features:
- Uninstall AI-related features and Microsoft Edge  
- Remove leftover files and registry keys  
- Disable additional bloatware services and scheduled tasks  
- Provides a safer, cleaner Windows environment optimized for gaming

### Warning:
Some features may affect system stability or functionality. Create a restore point before using.

### Usage:
Run as Administrator and choose the cleanup options from the menu.

---

Recommended for users who want a clean, fast, and lightweight Windows.
